{"tid":836064,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"發現d港女食起洋腸上黎真係世界級","createTime":"2018-09-25T11:19:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-25T13:12:56.000Z","uid":68626,"like":6,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c0b7481c2b71be30ef2112b70a3b0d9dd9616599","tid":836064,"uid":68626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T11:19:41.000Z","msg":"今日我地班上分組做project<br />\n之後同組黎左個法國仔 exchange<br />\n我地兩男兩女咁啦<br />\n本身都唔識對方<br />\n個法國仔個樣都ok ,但我應該大隻過佢，佢身形無我咁好<br />\n之後佢我地互相打招呼咁<br />\n個法國仔用d帶口音既英文 say hi 咁<br />\n咁我地又say hi，點知佢又係到親吻女同學隻手，又攬佢地咁，d女同學有少少驚訝咁，但都接受<br />\n之後我諗住有樣學樣啦<br />\n點知d女同學推開我話我死變態<br />\n呢個世界真係唔公平<br />\n人地做就得，我做就唔得"},{"pid":"f34f9ff4447f3339eb205345f1075b5be661121e","tid":836064,"uid":119145,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T11:20:52.000Z","msg":"喔"},{"pid":"daff9cbedd0c0756e4aaabed05952c870667591a","tid":836064,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T11:21:03.000Z","msg":"where find"},{"pid":"3f82e4d5a92d8c6d66a730e8907ce699eaf47082","tid":836064,"uid":38904,"like":20,"dislike":2,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T11:25:35.000Z","msg":"詭辯家最愛開po狙擊：<br />\n1 港女<br />\n2 asso仔<br />\n3 去台灣讀書嘅人<br />\n<br />\n歡迎補充"},{"pid":"9d606bfb6dca72d146000f1048f5f81e79bc04c9","tid":836064,"uid":198998,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T11:28:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fb7484d33f28750086d02d44d3272523c38b71e","tid":836064,"uid":31254,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T13:09:40.000Z","msg":"唔關國籍事<br />\n原因：<br />\nop係撚樣"},{"pid":"4b1248ba08871e2811a294452cae4a1cdfb32cb8","tid":836064,"uid":31749,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T13:11:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d0bcc8a76c5e0bdb67ab4140a6d5f5a4ad9a0257","tid":836064,"uid":30710,"like":0,"dislike